1
00:00:20,840 --> 00:00:22,320
Is there something wrong?

2
00:00:22,520 --> 00:00:23,680
Whoa.

3
00:00:24,120 --> 00:00:25,440
You picked up so fast.

4
00:00:25,520 --> 00:00:28,000
I bet it didn't even finish ringing once.

5
00:00:28,680 --> 00:00:30,320
So there's nothing wrong?

6
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:32,000
There is.

7
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:34,120
I called to report an incident.

8
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:37,440
Well?

9
00:00:38,480 --> 00:00:41,080
I couldn't sleep. What do I do?

10
00:00:46,040 --> 00:00:47,200
Couldn't sleep?

11
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:52,600
Couldn't sleep?

12
00:00:57,400 --> 00:01:00,440
And how can I help you with that?

13
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,120
Can you

14
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:05,200
keep me company for a while?

15
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:09,320
Maybe a conversation will make me sleepy.

16
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:12,960
Of course.

17
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,640
Whatever you want to talk about,

18
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:19,080
you can start.

19
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,120
Then...

20
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:29,120
can I tell you about me?

21
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:33,960
If it's information about you,

22
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:36,160
I already knew.

23
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,760
Tawan.

24
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,600
You can tell me.

25
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:50,400
Even if I already knew, I'll listen.

26
00:01:56,600 --> 00:02:02,880
I was so nervous about my audition
because there were so many talented people that year.

27
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:05,320
And the day before the final round of auditions,

28
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:09,000
I remember I got myositis
and my dad wouldn't let me go.

29
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:12,960
I was begging and crying like I was gonna die.

30
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:17,040
I almost followed my dream
without a home to come back to.

31
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:21,760
Back when I was a trainee, I trained so hard.

32
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:25,600
Did you know I trained at least eight hours a day?

33
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:29,280
Both singing and dancing.
Not to mention all the performances.

34
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:32,640
Oh, and I practiced on my own
because I'd messed up in training.

35
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:34,440
Ugh, it was so hard back then.

36
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,520
I slept only two or three hours a day.

37
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:42,160
That's not all. I have a lot more to tell you.

38
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:45,000
The path to become the people's female idol!

39
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,400
Tawan!

40
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:49,840
What happened?

41
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:53,960
The lights went out.

42
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,760
Please don't hang up.

43
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,360
The lights went out.

44
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:14,080
Tawan, the lights came back.

45
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:23,400
Tawan, I wanna go to an amusement park.

46
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:27,800
Even since I told you back then that I wanted to go,

47
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:30,080
believe it or not, I haven't gone yet.

48
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,840
Tawan?

49
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:44,200
-Yes?
-I'm almost at the door.

50
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,880
I don't see anyone out there.

51
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:50,560
Ayla, listen. You have to be careful.

52
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,800
And slowly walking there.

53
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:57,520
If you find something bad, scream.

54
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:02,960
I'm at the door.

55
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:05,960
Be careful.

56
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,000
Slowly.

57
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,640
Slowly.

58
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,120
Tawan.

59
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,399
It's morning.

60
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,720
I got you some congee.

61
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:30,680
How did you know...

62
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,680
that I love congee with pathongko?

63
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:38,560
I already told you I had all your information.

64
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,640
Tawan,

65
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,080
bullshit.

66
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:48,080
Some kid went on and on about her favorite foods.

67
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:53,120
Probably around

68
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:54,920
four in the morning.

69
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:01,880
This shop makes great congee.

70
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:06,640
I bought it and came straight here.

71
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:24,520
I think we need some caffeine.

72
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:27,440
My treat, because you just bought me congee.

73
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,400
Hey!

74
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,600
Ayla!

75
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:03,360
Tawan works a lot.
Doesn't her partner mind?

76
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:06,960
This is against the rules.
Boss shouldn't be doing this.

77
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:09,480
I think this whole thing is fishy.

78
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:13,880
Your life is now my duty and responsibility.

79
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:16,360
But if you're unhappy with how I work,

80
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:18,280
I'm willing to walk away.

81
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:24,680
♪ The closer we are, the further it feels ♪

82
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:28,040
♪ Never once ♪

83
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:31,960
♪ Did you notice ♪

84
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:35,760
♪ What my heart was feeling ♪

85
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:39,800
♪ When I look at you, my eyes say it all ♪

86
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:44,520
♪ Waiting only for you to pay me attention ♪

87
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:50,880
♪ My heart yells every day,
But its voice never reaches you ♪

88
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:54,880
♪ I want you to know how long I've kept this in ♪

89
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:59,560
♪ Do you have any idea ♪

90
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:02,200
♪ As each minute goes by ♪

91
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:07,960
♪ How much my heart wants to say I love you? ♪

92
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:25,160
♪ When I look at you, my eyes say it all ♪

93
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:29,760
♪ Do you have any idea ♪

94
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:32,520
♪ As each minute goes by ♪

95
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:38,880
♪ How much my heart wants to say I love you? ♪
